## tracking.py

Decorator that captures token usage from every API response and writes a `TokenUsageRecord`.

Token extraction per provider:
```python
# Gemini
input_tokens  = response.usage_metadata.prompt_token_count
output_tokens = response.usage_metadata.candidates_token_count

# Claude
input_tokens  = response.usage.input_tokens
output_tokens = response.usage.output_tokens
```

Cost delegated to `CostCalculator` from `src/models/metrics.py`.
Record persisted to `token_usage` table via `AdLibrary`.

